WEBVTT

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:32.640
The word jihad stands
for all those meanings as a whole.

00:01:34.920 --> 00:01:39.336
Jihad may at times
take the form of fighting,

00:01:39.360 --> 00:01:40.560
but only sometimes,

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:42.920
under strict conditions,

00:01:44.200 --> 00:01:46.160
within rules and limits.

00:01:47.840 --> 00:01:49.056
In Islam,

00:01:49.080 --> 00:01:54.080
the benefit of an act must outweigh
the harm or hardship it entails.

00:01:55.240 --> 00:01:56.976
More importantly,

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:01.736
the verses in the Koran
that are connected to jihad or fighting